---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section class="bg-light py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div data-animate>
      <SectionLabel text="How We Work" light />
    </div>

    <h2
      data-animate
      class="mt-4 max-w-3xl font-display text-4xl text-dark lg:text-5xl"
    >
      Built for businesses that solve real problems.
    </h2>

    <div data-animate class="mt-8 max-w-3xl space-y-4 text-base leading-loose text-muted">
      <p>
        Every engagement starts the same way: we listen. Before we write a
        single word, we learn your business, your audience, and your goals.
        Then we build a strategy you can see, understand, and hold us to.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our writers and editors produce content that sounds like you, only
        sharper, cleaner, and more persuasive. Every draft goes through
        rigorous review before it reaches you. And publishing is just the
        beginning. We monitor performance and refine continuously so your
        content compounds in value over time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
